---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-20 pb-10 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/images/backgrounds/bg-hero.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-dark-900/50 via-dark-900/80 to-dark-900"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Glow effects -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-blue/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-purple/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    <div class="inline-block mb-6 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10">
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-300">Transforma tu Relación con la IA</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
      AI Thinking, el método que
      <span class="gradient-text"> amplifica tu experiencia</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      El método que convierte 15 años de experiencia profesional en resultados que antes te tomaban semanas.
    <br/>
      En 4-6 semanas, dominas el sistema estratégico que separa a los que 'usan IA' de los que multiplican su impacto.
    </p>

    <!-- Cohort Info -->
    <div class="mb-8 inline-flex flex-col items-center gap-2 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue/10 to-accent-purple/10 border border-accent-blue/30">
      <div class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">
        Próxima cohorte: <span class="text-accent-blue">14 de enero, 2026</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-white/70">
        Solo 10 cupos | <span class="text-accent-cyan font-semibold">Quedan 2 disponibles</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
      <a
        href="/agendar"
        class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-blue to-accent-purple rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity glow"
      >
        Reservar mi lugar
      </a>
      <a
        href="/agendar"
        class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/20 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors"
      >
        Agendar llamada
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Amplification visual - centered below text -->
    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <picture>
        <source
          media="(max-width: 640px)"
          srcset="/images/backgrounds/amplificacion-mobile.webp"
          type="image/webp"
        />
        <source
          srcset="/images/backgrounds/amplificacion-desktop.webp"
          type="image/webp"
        />
        <img
          src="/images/backgrounds/amplificacion.png"
          alt="Amplificación"
          class="w-full"
          width="900"
          height="600"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </picture>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
